{"tid":141611,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲格：唔去巴塞 我首選永遠係阿仙奴","createTime":"2017-03-03T05:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T08:16:44.000Z","uid":37168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7940bf4914955520e1a465bdab458058782053e","tid":141611,"uid":37168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T05:07:53.000Z","msg":"香港時間3月2日，阿仙奴教練雲格的未來並不明晰，恰逢安歷基宣佈賽季後離開巴塞，媒體將教授和巴塞帥位聯繫了起來，但是雲格表示他不會執教巴塞。<br />\n<br />\n　　雲格出席了阿仙奴客戰利物浦的賽前記者會，他一上來就闢謠了自己將執教巴塞的傳聞。<br />\n<br />\n　　「<span style=\"color: red;\">我在阿仙奴已經20年了，我有很多次機會可以選擇離開，我覺得不必向你們承諾我會留在這裡。</span>所以你說我對巴塞的帥位有興趣嗎？根本沒有！」<br />\n<br />\n　　「<span style=\"color: red;\">我的優先選擇永遠是阿仙奴，所以根本不會去找別的工作</span>，我只選擇專注於自我，試著去向更高水平努力。」<br />\n<br />\n　　對於本週末與利物浦的硬仗，雲格也說出了一些值得注意的地方。<br />\n<br />\n　　「對我們來說，經過近兩週的調整，必須馬上找到比賽感覺，尤其是對利物浦這樣的球隊，從比賽一開始就要表現得強硬。」<br />\n<br />\n　　球員方面，雲格透露幾位傷員哥斯尼、基奧特以及藍斯都能回到球場，但是卡蘇拿目前的情況不是很理想。<br />\n<br />\n　　「他的傷勢很特殊，我不能確定他是否還能在賽季結束前復出，因為他現在甚至還不能做康復鍛鍊。這對我們來說是一個巨大的損失，從賽季開始的情況看，他本可能是今季的球隊最佳。」<br />\n<br />\n爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa2dff3bdb039047a6eb990414d4d85750bd492","tid":141611,"uid":4957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T05:09:33.000Z","msg":"Respect <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee750498b40cf7ebf6655cbd41dd93ac2220cbb","tid":141611,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T05:15:21.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺開哂綠燈畀雲伯伯教巴塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e15652e21e926759472bd950ba57d86b6f98c1cd","tid":141611,"uid":15140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T05:31:36.000Z","msg":"永續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd037540d6459ec1e9dd032ede93ac801901e7e1","tid":141611,"uid":38172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T05:34:02.000Z","msg":"點解你死都唔肯放過阿仙奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87fde66aa8e1ee1f983d691a3669cf39c3cf77a6","tid":141611,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T05:34:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>永續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n祝你下世雲加做你老豆 然後賣哂你d器官去幫屋企做裝修"},{"pid":"bc2a21dccfe20a20e717c10eebd439d332246209","tid":141611,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T05:42:33.000Z","msg":"Respect 雲yaya"},{"pid":"6b91e1b87bacd4c677e50dd47d6e9de705ba65aa","tid":141611,"uid":54109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T05:52:25.000Z","msg":"好似神奇隊長引退左都要痴實利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114bb7f2cff09612c5f60634347da9a70bee3b4a","tid":141611,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:49:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解你死都唔肯放過阿仙奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a492bc1930f3d872f87b6ad0ab95e2675f8285","tid":141611,"uid":4846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:16:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔</span></span>"}]}